<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-59-0473 </DOCNO><TEXT>Consideration is being given to the program of determining the operationalcharacteristics of NPP equipment for evaluation of parameter changes,testifying to equipment aging. Aging curve enabling to forecast the equipmentlifetime has been plotted on the base of measurement results. Choiceof measured parameters, applied methods of control, order of conductedmeasuremnts and method of equipment state prediction are discussed.</TEXT></DOC>